name: Interstellar(beyond)
description:
Endless interstellar, into the abyss of the universe, through the endless interstellar!
When you are driving a spaceship into the abyss of the universe, you will encounter many stars. Stay away from the stars through your sensitive reaction, preventing the spacecraft from hitting the stars, and eventually you will reach the finish line. People around the world are exploring the abyss of the universe. How far can you go? Compare with the global player!
